Hello Friend NG General informations This theme was highly inspired by the hello-friend and hermit. A lot of kudos for theier great work. Features Theming: dark/light mode, depending on your preferences (dark is default, but you can change it) Great reading experience thanks to Inter UI font, made by Rasmus Andersson Nice code highlighting thanks to PrismJS An easy way to modify the theme with Hugo tooling Fully responsive Support for social icons How to start You can download the theme manually by going to https://github.
